BFN 

  [Text] A royal decree has been issued appointing Major 
General Humaydi al-Fayiz military adviser and chief escort of 
His Majesty King Husayn as of 29 March 1994. 
  Maj. Gen. Humaydi al-Fayiz has occupied several leading 
positions in the Jordanian Armed Forces, among which are the 
commander of the Royal Guard and commander of the al-Husayn 
Bin-'Ali Brigade. 

